OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA widely dry and sunny day with
OL,6,Fany early morning low cloud and mist
OL,7,Fsoon clearing. Feeling very warm,
OL,8,Fespecially in the strong sunshine. A
OL,9,Fgentle easterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPlenty of late evening
OL,12,Fsunshine to end Wednesday. Largely
OL,13,Fclear skies overnight, though low
OL,14,Fcloud and mist potentially returning
OL,15,Fto eastern counties. A mild night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAnother fine, dry and very
OL,18,Fwarm day. Any morning low cloud once
OL,19,Fagain quickly clearing to leave
OL,20,Fprolonged periods of strong sunshine
OL,21,Fthroughout Thursday. Calm winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
