OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FStaying
OL,6,Fdry and settled into the weekend.
OL,7,FFurther sunny spells, though cloud
OL,8,Famounts generally increasing.
OL,9,FTemperatures slowly dropping, but
OL,10,Fstill feeling warm in the sunshine.
